# wandb beta leet run

## 

​

Usage
    
    
    run [OPTIONS] [PATH]
    

## 

​

Description

Launch the LEET TUI. LEET is a terminal UI for viewing a W&B run specified by an optional PATH. PATH can include a .wandb file or a run directory containing a .wandb file. If PATH is not provided, the command will look for the latest run.

## 

​

Arguments

Name| Default| Type  
---|---|---  
`path`| STR| False  
  
## 

​

Options

Flag| Type| Description  
---|---|---  
`-h, --help`| BOOL Flag| Show this message and exit. **Default** : False  
  
